<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> Elberse, Anita. <a href="http://hbr.harvardbusiness.org/2008/07/should-you-invest-in-the-long-tail/ar/1" class="external text" title="http://hbr.harvardbusiness.org/2008/07/should-you-invest-in-the-long-tail/ar/1" rel="nofollow">"Should You Invest in the Long Tail?"</a> <i><a href="/wiki/Harvard_Business_Review" title="Harvard Business Review">Harvard Business Review</a></i>, July–August 2008. (Full online article for purchase only.)</li>
